# Histograms for different set types in Squash App

### Who

<!--Who does this benefit or who will this affect? Who should be able to view this?-->

- New Yamb players

### What

<!--What problem needs addressing?-->

- Currently, the scoresheet table exists without an explanation of how it works, which works fine with players familiar to the game, but isn't very user friendly for new users. 
- Therefore, we should create a rules explanation for users to see. 

### Why

<!--What value does this add?-->

- If we have a ruleset available, more players could be encouraged to try and play. 

### Acceptance Criteria

<!--Testable done conditions; avoid implementation detail.-->

- [ ] The rules of the game are described and documented on the app
- [ ] (Optional) If a player has fewer than 5 games played, they are prompted to view the rules.